Privacy Policy
• Flatcracker Software LLC is committed to respecting your privacy.
• Flatcracker Software LLC will not sell or transmit to others any personally identifiable data entered into Period Plus.
• Flatcracker Software LLC will monitor Period Plus App usage only for administration, abuse prevention and support purposes.
• Flatcracker Software LLC uses data collected from the Period Polls feature with your consent in an aggregate manner to provide its users with helpful information.
• Flatcracker Software LLC does not sell or transmit Apple HealthKit data with any third parties.
• Occasionally Flatcracker Software might publish aggregate statistical studies and non identifying data in the form of articles published on its site, scientific articles, blogs, conferences or books from the Period Polls feature.
• If you have any concerns about our privacy policy, please send your comments or questions to
flatcracker @ gmail.com